ang film Perfect Strangers itu masih merasa semua berjalan baik-baik saja. \"Saya belum lihat (ketegangan) itu sih, mungkin belum terlalu dekat kali ya (waktu persalinan). Cuma dia sudah kelihatan kesulitan banget, perutnya gede banget, tidurnya sudah kesulitan, terus dia sering kebangun. Bayinya sudah gerak-gerak banget jadi dia kurang tidur aja,\" ceritanya mengenai kondisi istri. Melihat perjuangan istri mengandung, Denny Sumargo tak lantas diam saja. Dia mengaku kerap memberikan perhatian yang memang dibutuhkan oleh Olivia Allan. \"Ya standarlah nggak perlu banyak motivasi-motivasi berlebihan, cukup prepare, kadang-kadang elus perutnya ya, kadang-kadang kalau dia malam nggak enak tidurnya terus kebangun ya temenin,\" kata Denny Sumargo. Perjuangan Olivia Allan hingga akhirnya mengandung, tidaklah mudah. Oliva Allan mengalami 3 kali keguguran dan membuatnya sangat sedih.   \n","\n","                    author  \n","0          Mauludi Rismoyo  \n","1            prih febriani  \n","2  Muhammad Ahsan Nurrijal  \n","3             Dicky Ardian  \n","4  Febryantino Nur Pratama  "],"text/html":["\n","  <div id=\"df-1dd3bc22-fccd-4578-be6a-fddac61601ab\" class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","    <div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n","        vertical-align: top;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe thead th {\n","        text-align: right;\n","    }\n","</style>\n","<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n","  <thead>\n","    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n","      <th></th>\n","      <th>_id</th>\n","      <th>title</th>\n","      <th>category</th>\n","      <th>publish_date</th>\n","      <th>article_url</th>\n","      <th>content</th>\n","      <th>author</th>\n","    </tr>\n","  </thead>\n","  <tbody>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>0</th>\n","      <td>672389536403ebe3a5d75ca5</td>\n","      <td>Pentingnya Hak Cipta dan Perlakuan Maksimal untuk Para Pela